PortOS will be a portable embeddable small operating system that can run on mmu-less systems or systems with a mmu.


It will follow the System V ABI, and mostly be posix compilant to the extend that porting software becomes easier.

the memory model will use virtual address space paging on mmu systems

mmu stuff and security in user space
 
inspirations: {net, open, 4.4}bsd, lk, linux, toaruos, minix, xv6, minix





fast embeddable portable usable secure small hybird elf kernel that can run on mmu-less systems or systems with mmu.
